{"title_page": "Apollo\u2013Soyuz Test Project", "text_new": "{{Use mdy dates|date=November 2013}}\n{{Infobox spaceflight\n| name                  = Apollo\u2013Soyuz Test Project\n<!--image of the spacecraft/mission-->\n| image                 = Apollo-Soyuz-Test-Program-artist-rendering.jpg\n| image_caption         = A 1973 artist's conception of the docking of the two spacecraft\n| image_alt             = Painting of crew, spacecraft, and launch rockets\n| image_size            = <!--include px/em; defaults to 220px-->\n<!--mission insignia or patch-->\n| insignia              = Apollo-Soyuz Test Project patch.svg\n| insignia_caption      = Official emblem of the Apollo-Soyuz Test Project (ASTP) chosen by NASA and the Soviet Academy of Sciences\n| insignia_alt          = <!--image alt text-->\n| insignia_size         = <!--include px/em; defaults to 180px-->\n<!--Basic details-->\n| mission_type          = Cooperative/scientific\n| operator              = [[NASA]]\n| COSPAR_ID             = {{unbulleted list\n  |Soyuz: {{COSPAR|1975-065A}}\n  |Apollo: {{COSPAR|1975-066A}}\n}}\n| SATCAT                = {{unbulleted list|Soyuz: 8030|Apollo: 8032}}\n| mission_duration      = {{unbulleted list\n                            |Soyuz: 5 d 22 h 30 m\n                            |Apollo: 9 d 01 h 28 min\n                          }}\n<!-- This \"fun\" statistic is really unnecessary:\n| distance_travelled    = {{unbulleted list|Apollo: ~{{convert|5990000|km|mi|abbr=on}}\n                        | Soyuz: ~{{convert|3900000|km|mi|abbr=on}}}}-->\n| orbits_completed      = {{unbulleted list|Apollo: 148\n                                           |Soyuz: 96}}\n<!--Spacecraft properties-->\n| spacecraft            = {{unbulleted list|[[Apollo Command/Service Module|Apollo CSM]]-111\n                                           |Soyuz 19 }}\n| spacecraft_type       = {{unbulleted list|Apollo: Block II Apollo CSM and Apollo Docking Module\n                          |Soyuz: [[Soyuz 7